contentrichtext.text: '''ash-Sharqiyah''' ({{lang-ar|'''الشرقية'''}} ''the eastern'') may refer to: *[[Ash Sharqiyah Region (Oman)]] *[[Ash Sharqiyah Province]], Saudi Arabia *[[Ash Sharqiyah (town)]], Palestinian town near [[Jerusalem]] *[[Kassala (state)]], Sudan *[[Sharqia Governorate]], Egypt *[[Wadi ash-Sharqiyah]], [[Sudan]] *[[Mashriq]] ==See also== *[[Al Gharbiyah (disambiguation)]] (western) *[[Ash Shamaliyah (disambiguation)]] (northern) *[[Al Janobiyah (disambiguation)]] (southern) *[[Al Wusta (disambiguation)]] (central) *[[Eastern (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}} [[Category:Arabic words and phrases]]
